{"title":"Wear Your Bike Like a Backpack w/ Restrap’s New Hike-a-Bike Harness","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wear-your-bike-like-a-backpack-restrap-hike-a-bike-harness/","date":1681473385000,"content":"<p>Sometimes you just have to get off and push. Technical <a href=\"https://us.restrap.com/\" target=\"_blank\">bikepacking gear specialists</a>, Restrap know this, so they’ve launched a brand new outdoor product they’re sure you’ve never seen before. It’s a new way to carry your steed on super rough terrain… introducing the new Hike-A-Bike harness. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This product is aimed at riders who love heading out on trails that are rugged, with long un-ridable, hike-a-bike sections where the bike may need to be carried up very steep grades or over unrideable terrain. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-ready-to-carry-e1681420219119.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-ready-to-carry-e1681420219119-800x698.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness ready to carry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-ready-to-carry-e1681420219119-800x698.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-ready-to-carry-e1681420219119-297x259.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-ready-to-carry-e1681420219119-120x105.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-ready-to-carry-e1681420219119-768x670.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-ready-to-carry-e1681420219119.jpeg 1276w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Restrap</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-side-view.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-side-view-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness side view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-side-view-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-side-view-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-side-view-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-side-view-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-side-view.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Restrap</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-from-behind.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-from-behind-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness in use from behind\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-from-behind-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-from-behind-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-from-behind-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-from-behind-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-from-behind.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Restrap says that the Hike-A-Bike Harness is a quick and easy fit to most bikes, giving the ability to go from riding your bike to carrying your bike and back again a snap. When the rider has the bike strapped to the harness, it allows your hands to be free for balance or moving obstacles.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-by-itself.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-by-itself-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness on bike by itself\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-by-itself-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-by-itself-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-by-itself-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-by-itself-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-by-itself.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-with-frame-bag.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-with-frame-bag-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness on bike with frame bag\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-with-frame-bag-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-with-frame-bag-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-with-frame-bag-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-with-frame-bag-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-on-bike-with-frame-bag.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When it is tucked away on the top tube, it remains out of the way and will not interfere with your riding. It uses adjustable mounting points allowing the lightweight design to be custom tailored to fit your bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-vegan-friendly-lable-e1681419814684.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"626\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-vegan-friendly-lable-e1681419814684-800x626.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness vegan friendly lable\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-vegan-friendly-lable-e1681419814684-800x626.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-vegan-friendly-lable-e1681419814684-297x232.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-vegan-friendly-lable-e1681419814684-120x94.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-vegan-friendly-lable-e1681419814684-768x601.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-vegan-friendly-lable-e1681419814684.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-quick-strap-e1681419870964.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"586\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-quick-strap-e1681419870964-800x586.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness quick strap\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-quick-strap-e1681419870964-800x586.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-quick-strap-e1681419870964-297x217.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-quick-strap-e1681419870964-120x88.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-quick-strap-e1681419870964-768x562.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-quick-strap-e1681419870964.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The harness is made of durable TPU coated Nylon and finished with a vegan-friendly PU Restrap label and comes with two retention straps and a long fast strap to secure the front wheel. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness up a steel hill\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-up-a-steel-hill.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Restrap Hike-A-Bike Harness in use outside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Restrap-Hike-A-Bike-Harness-in-use-outside.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Restrap</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Hike-A-Bike Harness Features and Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail; $79.99</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Quick and easy harness to fit most bikes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Go from riding to carrying and back in a matter of seconds</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Allows you to walk up tough hike-a-bike terrain, hands-free and well balanced</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Doesn’t get in the way while riding</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Breathable padded section which keeps the bike comfortable on your shoulders</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Adjustable mounting points using super-strong modified Fast Straps to tailor the fit to most bikes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Extra long Fast Strap included to hold the front wheel in line, to prevent swing.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Made from waterproof TPU-coated Nylon.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Weight: 235g</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check it out and other goodies by hitting the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://us.restrap.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Us.Restrap.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wear-your-bike-like-a-backpack-restrap-hike-a-bike-harness/\">Wear Your Bike Like a Backpack w/ Restrap’s New Hike-a-Bike Harness</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"bc7d9677f87ea9f79694df507803ba7e147f84c95a7ca3b